WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.990 align:middle line:90%


00:00:00.990 --> 00:00:05.040 align:middle line:10%
- Spring forward, fall
back could be no more.

00:00:05.040 --> 00:00:09.150 align:middle line:10%
Daylight Saving Time in
the US could be permanent.

00:00:09.150 --> 00:00:11.670 align:middle line:84%
Most Americans say they
are tired of moving

00:00:11.670 --> 00:00:15.420 align:middle line:84%
the clocks twice a year and
we should just pick one.

00:00:15.420 --> 00:00:19.390 align:middle line:84%
But did the government
pick the wrong one?

00:00:19.390 --> 00:00:21.495 align:middle line:90%
This is a Gaia News Breakdown.

00:00:21.495 --> 00:00:24.385 align:middle line:90%
